scenes.description: Ending of the track and field segment with Marine and Miko collapsed on the track.
Intro and performance of the 'Marin-chan Switch' segment, where Marine does poses for Amane Kanata to guess.
Start of the 'Hololive Soap Opera' skit featuring Marine as the mother, Aqua as the daughter, and Shion as the boyfriend.
